1
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:20,000
CMCT發佈

2
00:00:43,870 --> 00:00:45,990
未來
The future

3
00:00:46,070 --> 00:00:48,390
南北極冰水徹底融化
The polar ice caps have melted

4
00:00:48,430 --> 00:00:51,190
地球被淹沒在海洋中
covering the Earth with water

5
00:00:51,270 --> 00:00:55,750
倖存者逐漸建立一個新世界
Those who survived have adapted...

6
00:00:55,830 --> 00:00:57,750
"水世界"
to a new world.

7
00:05:12,305 --> 00:05:14,000
我沒上你船[印地語]

8
00:05:14,774 --> 00:05:16,264
我不會幹那種事的

9
00:05:16,343 --> 00:05:18,208
你下去了很長時間

10
00:05:18,812 --> 00:05:20,370
我的船出了點問題

11
00:05:21,348 --> 00:05:26,285
破了一個大洞 幸好還有地方讓我呼吸

12
00:05:26,590 --> 00:05:30,030
夠倒霉的 說英語吧
Bad luck, English.

13
00:05:30,110 --> 00:05:34,550
最近那些販奴商生產出了一種效果很好的氧化劑
But the Slavers are producing a good grade of poxy these days.

14
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:37,510
跟你換一把泥土 或是那個風鈴
Cost you a handful of dirt... or maybe that wind chime.

15
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:41,390
- 你來這媟F嘛? - 等你唄
- What are you doin' here? - Just waiting.

16
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:44,430
你的臭手別碰船帆
Take your hand off the sail.

17
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:47,070
手拿開
Take it off!

18
00:05:47,150 --> 00:05:50,830
我之前見過你的船 卻沒見過你
I've seen your boat before. Haven't seen you.

19
00:05:52,070 --> 00:05:54,670
是合法的先占
Took it legal.

20
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:57,710
我發現這船的時候船主已經死了
Previous owner was dead on the tiller when I found it.

21
00:05:57,745 --> 00:06:00,670
我高價轉賣之前你還有一個小時的時間考慮
You had another hour before I traded up again.

22
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:03,390
賺得更多是我的宗旨
Just improving my means.

23
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:07,270
- 好吧 算我欠你個人情 - 謝啦 不用了
- Well, I owe you then. - No, thanks.

24
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:12,510
我的裝備已經補足了 我才從一個環礁基地出來
I got all the supplies I need. Just came from an atoll.

25
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:15,550
你想去的話 向東航行八天
Eight days east, if you're interested.

26
00:06:17,710 --> 00:06:21,430
- 海行者碰面通常都要交換 - 我知道規矩
- Two drifters meet, something needs to be exchanged. - I know the code.

27
00:06:21,470 --> 00:06:24,150
但是這次我就免費給你
But I'll give you this one for free.

28
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:27,590
在這片汪洋中絕不會有免費午餐的
Nothing's free in Waterworld.

29
00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:28,910
是啊
Ha-ha. Yeah.

30
00:06:28,945 --> 00:06:30,150
是啊
Ha-ha. Yeah.

31
00:06:40,590 --> 00:06:42,790
是掠海者
Smokers.

32
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:44,870
風勢正好助我順利開溜
Just enough wind to get away clean.

33
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:50,790
就別管那包東西了
Forget the bag.

34
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:58,710
那不值得你一搏 更何況你連帆都沒拉起來
It's not worth it. You'll never make it with your sails down.

35
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:01,350
Hey!

36
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:15,390
祝你好運啦
What can I say?

37
00:07:35,550 --> 00:07:38,830
- 喬 他要開溜 - 搞什麼鬼?
- Joe, he's goin' for it. - What the hell?

38
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,910
真是大開眼界啊
Never seen that before.

39
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,990
快啟動 快啊 快踩油門
Here we go! Go! Drive! Drive!

40
00:07:57,270 --> 00:08:00,270
快點 再快點
Faster! Faster! Whoo!

41
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:23,350
快點 要被他搶走了
Come on! He's gonna get it! He's gonna get it!

42
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:45,310
- 快逮他 - 上呀! 上呀!
- Pick her up! - Get it! Get it!

43
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:16,750
不 別
Oh, no!

44
00:10:02,990 --> 00:10:05,910
有船接近 到門外了
Inbound! Straight out from the gates.

45
00:10:13,673 --> 00:10:14,799
你講什麼話?

46
00:10:15,470 --> 00:10:17,430
英文
English.

47
00:10:19,950 --> 00:10:24,030
已經收市了 海行者 今天已經不再交易了
Flag's down, drifter. We got enough traders.

48
00:10:31,558 --> 00:10:33,287
他拿的是什麼?

49
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:40,430
泥土
Dirt.

50
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:42,430
開門
Open the gates!

51
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:27,070
化骨為漿
Bones to berries.

52
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:29,390
抽脈為藤
Veins to vine.

53
00:11:29,470 --> 00:11:33,630
肢骨化為大樹 血漿變鹽水
These tendons to trees. This blood to brine.

54
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:35,390
歲月奪走了她的生命
Too old she was.

55
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:38,210
但她卻恩澤予我們
This woman does leave us

56
00:11:38,290 --> 00:11:42,870
我們在上帝面前收下她的恩澤並銘記她
ecycled and enshrined in the presence of Him who leads us.

57
00:12:00,950 --> 00:12:05,510
那是什麼?
What is that?

58
00:12:09,950 --> 00:12:12,470
你認識我嗎?
You know me?

59
00:12:12,550 --> 00:12:14,470
我知道你是誰
I know what you are.

60
00:12:14,550 --> 00:12:18,190
很好 那你自然知道在這兒鬧事
Good. Then you know if you look for trouble while you're here,

61
00:12:18,230 --> 00:12:20,470
只會讓你吃不完兜著走
you'll find more than you can handle.

62
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:24,190
我給你兩個小時
You got two hours.

63
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:28,830
我只需要一小時
I'll only need one.

64
00:12:38,950 --> 00:12:41,510
他走過來了
He's comin' over here.

65
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:48,870
- 給我 - 賞你們一人一個
- Me. - You each get one...

66
00:12:48,950 --> 00:12:51,510
只要能在我回來前幫我看好船
if everything's here when I get back.

67
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:02,070
純泥土
Pure dirt.

68
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:04,630
3.2公斤
3.2 kilos.

69
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:09,830
你從哪兒找來這麼多泥土?
How'd you come by so much of it?

70
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:12,710
從這兒向西差不多30個海平線遠的另一個環礁基地那兒
Another atoll 30 horizons west of here.

71
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:14,870
那他們是在哪兒弄到的呢
Where'd they get it?

72
00:13:14,950 --> 00:13:18,110
- 他們沒有透露 - 聽說那地方的人
- They didn't say. - We heard about that place...

73
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:20,790
全都被殺光了
that they was all killed.

74
00:13:22,590 --> 00:13:24,790
- 那就是他們不透露的原因 - 掠海者干的?
- That's why they didn't say. - Smokers?

75
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:28,030
也許是掠海者 也有可能是販奴商
Maybe Smokers, maybe Slavers.

76
00:13:29,590 --> 00:13:32,230
怎麼樣?要交易嗎?
So what's the word? We tradin' or not?

77
00:13:32,310 --> 00:13:37,110
我們就把它當成是 純淨水的價值交易
We'll tally it like, uh, pure hydro.

78
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:43,710
給你62塊錢
Works out to... 62 chits.

79
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:48,630
我要加倍
I want twice that.

80
00:13:52,310 --> 00:13:56,350
- 我只想喝一點水罷了 - 不行 除非你告訴我
- I just want one sip of hydro! - No, not 'til you tell me.

81
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:59,790
她背上有圖案 我看過
She got inkings on her back. I seen her.

82
00:13:59,830 --> 00:14:02,990
傳說只要你能解開那孩子身上圖案之謎
They say if you read the marks on the child,

83
00:14:03,030 --> 00:14:06,590
那就能指引你到達陸地
they'll lead ya all the way to Dryland.

84
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:09,750
- 陸地只是神話 - 但還是有人相信
- Dryland's a myth. - Some still believe.

85
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:12,870
他們還說掠海者在找這小女孩
They say the Smokers even got an eye out for her.

86
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:17,670
是嗎 那麼 我們最好還是保密
Well, then, we'd better keep it to ourselves.

87
00:14:25,691 --> 00:14:27,591
挺壯嘛

88
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:44,190
- 需要幫忙嗎 - 是的
- Help you? - Yeah.

89
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:46,670
- 商店在哪? - 就你眼前
- Where's the store? - You found it.

90
00:14:52,310 --> 00:14:54,230
東西不多
You don't have much.

91
00:14:55,590 --> 00:14:58,110
你就是帶著泥土的那個人?
You the man with the dirt?

92
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:17,190
乾杯
Skoal.

93
00:15:20,910 --> 00:15:23,350
- 再來一杯 - 來兩杯
- One more. - Make it two.

94
00:15:23,430 --> 00:15:27,230
一個這麼有錢的人會請陸上的朋友喝一杯的 我確定
A man this rich will buy for a fellow outwater, I'm sure.

95
00:15:27,310 --> 00:15:29,750
就一杯
One.

96
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:35,990
你腳上這雙鞋挺有趣的
That's an interesting pair of boots you got.

97
00:15:36,070 --> 00:15:38,190
- 想交換嗎? - 不想
- Trade? - No.

98
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:40,350
真可惜
Shame.

99
00:15:45,872 --> 00:15:46,770
就是她
That's her

100
00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:50,070
埃諾拉 你在幹嘛?
Enola. Hey, what are you doing?

101
00:15:50,110 --> 00:15:51,390
不行 你不能這樣
No, you can't do that.

102
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,670
我還需要一塊兒
I need another piece.

103
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:53,950
我想多畫點
I want to draw some more.

104
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:56,710
我會拿給你的 去後面呆著去
I'll get it to you. Just stay in the back.

105
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:59,870
用這筆錢 你能好好沖個澡
With all those chits, you could order up a bath.

106
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:01,210
你用淡水洗過澡嗎?
Have you ever had a freshwater bath?

107
00:16:01,210 --> 00:16:02,470
你為什麼找我說話?
Why are you talkin' to me?

108
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:04,470
我只想交個朋友
Just being friendly.

109
00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:12,150
- 那是蕃茄樹嗎? - 對
- Is that a tomato plant? - Yeah.

110
00:16:12,230 --> 00:16:14,390
你很有眼光啊
You have a keen eye.

111
00:16:14,430 --> 00:16:16,470
曾經在圖片上見過 怎麼賣的?
Saw one in a picture. How much?

112
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,790
你一半的錢
Half your chits.

113
00:16:36,270 --> 00:16:39,310
- 那些我也要 - 還要什麼?
- I'll take them too. - Take what?

114
00:16:39,390 --> 00:16:42,390
- 東西全被你買了 - 那些架子我也要
- You bought everything. - I'll take them shelves.

115
00:16:44,990 --> 00:16:48,390
你在海上那15個月堻ㄗㄗ儦L什麼
So, what did you see out there in your 15 months?

116
00:16:48,470 --> 00:16:51,030
- 比如呢? - 這片水域的盡頭
- Such as? - An end to all this water.

117
00:16:51,110 --> 00:16:54,710
你問錯人了
Askin' the wrong person.

118
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:56,790
他們今天不是埋葬了一個人嗎?
The one they buried today?

119
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:59,270
她就是這兒的唯一盡頭
She found the only end there is.

120
00:17:04,430 --> 00:17:06,350
航海人 我給你一個建議
I've got a proposition for you, Mariner.

121
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:09,963
我不會留下來
I'm not staying. 

122
00:17:09,963 --> 00:17:11,616
我們沒要你留下來
We're not asking you to.

123
00:17:11,616 --> 00:17:13,270
我們要的是你的後裔
All we want is your seed.

124
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:17,470
找自己人雖然也行
We can look to our own for impregnation,

125
00:17:17,510 --> 00:17:22,990
但是長此以往必會導致孩子的基因不良
but too much of that sort of thing gets... undesirable.

126
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:26,030
只要她懷了孕
When she's pregnant

127
00:17:26,110 --> 00:17:28,790
你就可以帶上你所需的所有補給繼續你的行程
you go on your way with all the supplies you need.

128
00:17:28,870 --> 00:17:32,830
別費神了 你們已經無藥可救了
You don't have anything. You're dying.

129
00:17:37,390 --> 00:17:41,150
沒有人會在漂泊那麼久之後竟對女人無動於衷的
No man stays out that long and turns down a woman.

130
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:46,830
- 他一定在隱瞞什麼 - 說不定他是個掠海者間諜
- He's hiding something. - Maybe he's a Smoker spy.

131
00:17:57,230 --> 00:18:00,350
只有長老讓你走 你才能走
When the elders say so, you can leave,

132
00:18:00,430 --> 00:18:02,350
否則別想走
and not before.

133
00:18:21,510 --> 00:18:23,430
有鰓
Gills.

134
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:28,510
- 變種人 - 他是變種人
- Mutation! - He's a mutant!

135
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:31,390
我的手
My hand!

136
00:18:46,590 --> 00:18:49,070
快撒網
Throw the nets!

137
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:23,470
你憑什麼?
By what right...

138
00:19:24,990 --> 00:19:27,910
憑你雇我來維持這堛滲揮
You pay me to keep the peace.

139
00:19:27,990 --> 00:19:29,910
絕不是這樣的秩序
This isn't it.

140
00:19:29,990 --> 00:19:33,310
- 他已經殺了我們一個人了 - 他只是自衛
- He has killed one of ours. - He was defending himself.

141
00:19:33,390 --> 00:19:34,643
他必須被處決
He needs to be destroyed!

142
00:19:34,643 --> 00:19:35,896
宰了他 我們得宰了他
Kill him. Let's kill him.

143
00:19:35,896 --> 00:19:37,150
也許吧
That may be,

144
00:19:37,230 --> 00:19:40,470
但絕不是在這兒更不是用這種方式
but not here and not like this.

145
00:20:12,550 --> 00:20:14,470
那是什麼?
What is it?

146
00:20:14,505 --> 00:20:16,470
該死的
Damn.

147
00:20:17,670 --> 00:20:20,950
他們看得太緊了 我沒機會下手
It's tied. I can't get it off.

148
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:27,630
開門
Open the gate.

149
00:20:59,030 --> 00:21:02,310
那是地圖嗎?
Is it a map?

150
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:06,110
如果你知道就告訴我 好嗎 埃諾拉?
You'd tell me if you knew, wouldn't you, Enola?

151
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:12,390
- 你在畫什麼? - 我不知道
- What are you drawing? - I don't know.

152
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:18,310
海倫 你看 看這小天才的最新幻想
Helen, look. Look at the prodigal child's latest vision.

153
00:21:24,070 --> 00:21:26,610
我們什麼時候才能走? 
How soon before we can leave?

154
00:21:26,610 --> 00:21:29,150
我還不知道幾時能走?
I don't have any idea yet where we can go.

155
00:21:29,230 --> 00:21:32,510
我搞不懂她的刺青
I haven't figured out the tattoo on her back.

156
00:21:32,550 --> 00:21:36,230
我真是個蠢蛋 答案看似近在眼前
I'm a stupid man. The answer's right there.

157
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:38,310
實則遠在天邊
It's just beyond me.

158
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:43,390
也許他知道
Maybe he knows.

159
00:21:52,150 --> 00:21:56,550
是的我看到了那是蹼
Oh, yes, I see. They are webbed.

160
00:21:56,630 --> 00:21:58,530
1 2 3 4 5 6 7
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven,

161
00:21:58,530 --> 00:22:00,430
8 9 有10個趾頭 真不可思議
eight, nine, ten digits. That's wonderful.

162
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:03,470
他們說你有鰓
They tell me, too, that you have gills.

163
00:22:03,550 --> 00:22:08,270
排列整齊的鰓 是已經退化還是真的有用?
Isotropic gills. Are they merely vestigial or are they functional now?

164
00:22:08,310 --> 00:22:11,750
我叫葛雷格 我是說過來給你點
My name is Gregor. I've just come to pay you a little vi... vi...

165
00:22:13,390 --> 00:22:16,590
老天啊
Oh, my God.

166
00:22:16,670 --> 00:22:19,750
抱歉 我不是笑你
I'm sorry. I'm not laughing at you.

167
00:22:19,830 --> 00:22:22,830
只是有點興奮 你的鰓能用
I'm excited. Your gills. They're functional.

168
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:26,590
大自然的鬼斧神工啊 你能在水堜I吸
Icthyus sapien. You can breathe in the water.

169
00:22:26,670 --> 00:22:30,550
你能潛多深?
How deep can you go? Look, I'm only here...

170
00:22:30,630 --> 00:22:33,230
我來這兒只是想來好好瞭解下你
Look, l'm only here because I want to learn more about you.

171
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:45,390
我也不怪你 告訴我
I can't say that I blame you. But tell me:

172
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:54,150
- 我沒有同族 - 噢 那就是魚式退化
- I have no "kind." - Oh, fish rot.

173
00:22:54,230 --> 00:22:57,590
我好奇地是之前沒有 還是現在沒有呢
I'd be surprised if there weren't others, and if there aren't,

174
00:22:57,630 --> 00:23:01,110
還是最終會有呢
there will be eventually.

175
00:23:01,190 --> 00:23:04,470
唔 我來是因為有個問題要問你
Anyway, I've come here because I need to ask you a question.

176
00:23:04,510 --> 00:23:08,470
你的泥土從哪兒來的?
Where... Where did your dirt come from?

177
00:23:08,510 --> 00:23:10,870
從陸地來的嗎?
Is it from Dryland?

178
00:23:11,110 --> 00:23:13,190
你看得懂這個嗎?
Do you know what this is?

179
00:23:15,150 --> 00:23:17,510
古時候的人做了壞事 是不是
The ancients... They did something terrible, didn't they?

180
00:23:17,550 --> 00:23:21,350
才導致了這個滿是水的世界 就在幾百 好幾百年前
To cause all this water. Hundreds... Hundreds of years ago.

181
00:23:21,390 --> 00:23:24,430
如果我告訴了你 你肯開鎖嗎?
If I tell you, will you open this lock?

182
00:23:26,870 --> 00:23:29,750
我沒鑰匙
I haven't a key.

183
00:23:29,830 --> 00:23:32,590
- 這下面有一個繫纜耳 - 什麼?
- There's a mooring cleat down there. - What?

184
00:23:32,630 --> 00:23:35,670
- 那勝過任何鑰匙 - 繫纜耳?
- Good as any key. - A mooring cleat?

185
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:40,550
我不會傷害任何人 我只想離開
I won't hurt anyone. I'll just leave.

186
00:23:45,310 --> 00:23:47,310
你在那媟F嘛?
What's your business there?

187
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:49,470
- 快走吧 - 我不是個有膽識的人
- Move along! - I'm not a brave man.

188
00:23:49,550 --> 00:23:53,750
如果你真知道陸地的事 請告訴我 求你了
If you know anything about Dryland, please tell me. Please!

189
00:23:55,190 --> 00:23:57,190
別把它帶進墳墓
Don't let it die with you.

190
00:23:57,230 --> 00:23:59,830
不 別 別 別 停下來!
No, no, no, no. Stop!

191
00:24:43,750 --> 00:24:47,270
我們決定這名變種人
it is our decision that this mute-o...

192
00:24:47,350 --> 00:24:50,550
的確對我們造成威脅
does, indeed, constitute a threat.

193
00:24:50,590 --> 00:24:53,590
因此為了公共安全
Therefore, in the interest of public safety,

194
00:24:53,630 --> 00:24:57,230
他被判處回收之刑
he is hereby sentenced to be recycled...

195
00:24:57,310 --> 00:25:00,190
遵照慣例執行
in the customary fashion.

196
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:01,990
行刑
Proceed.

197
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:10,790
抱歉了
I'm sorry.

198
00:25:14,630 --> 00:25:16,710
化骨為漿
Bones to berries.

199
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:19,430
抽脈為藤
Veins to vines.

200
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:23,270
肢骨化為大樹 血漿變鹽水
His tendons to trees. His blood to brine.

201
00:25:23,350 --> 00:25:26,430
他的生命詭異而怪誕
Too strange for life he was.

202
00:25:26,510 --> 00:25:30,910
變種人即將離我們而去
This mute-o now does leave us,

203
00:25:30,950 --> 00:25:33,830
我們在神明面前收下他的恩澤並銘記他
recycled and entombed, in the presence of him who leads us.

204
00:25:47,030 --> 00:25:51,790
是掠海者 正從太陽的方向攻過來了
Smokers! Dead out of the sun!

205
00:25:54,910 --> 00:25:58,470
大家各就各位
To your posts!

206
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:15,990
老天啊 偶滴神啊
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

207
00:26:26,430 --> 00:26:29,030
- 大開殺戒 - 進攻
- Kill! - There!

208
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:41,950
在城牆內很安全
We are safe behind these walls.

209
00:26:43,550 --> 00:26:45,470
是吧?
Aren't we?

210
00:26:51,350 --> 00:26:54,390
放我出來!
Let me out!

211
00:26:55,990 --> 00:26:58,430
讓我也出來戰鬥
Let me out! I'll fight!

212
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,750
傳令下去開始攻城
Give me the key to the city now.

213
00:27:33,590 --> 00:27:35,870
我們上 開攻了 開攻了
Let's go! Let's go! Let's go!

214
00:27:38,630 --> 00:27:41,510
上膛 上膛 快
Floor it! Floor it! Floor it!

215
00:28:02,710 --> 00:28:05,030
快疏通 給我弄通
Swab it! Swab it!

216
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:08,790
再裝子彈
Goddamn! More ammo!

217
00:28:23,150 --> 00:28:25,150
把門撞開來
Break down the door!

218
00:28:29,030 --> 00:28:32,070
老天爺啊!
My God!

219
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:34,630
Ha!

220
00:28:36,830 --> 00:28:39,830
速戰速決拿下這座環礁基地
We'll have this atoll in no time.

221
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:44,990
轉起來!轉起來
Crank it! Crank it!

222
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:51,430
注意!
Look!

223
00:29:10,030 --> 00:29:12,150
當心
Look out!

224
00:29:34,790 --> 00:29:36,750
噢 不要啊
Oh, no!

225
00:29:47,670 --> 00:29:50,510
繼續充氣 讓它們鼓起來
You get that goin'! Fill 'em up!

226
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:31,750
海倫 快過來
Helen, come quickly!

227
00:30:31,790 --> 00:30:33,910
海倫
Helen!

228
00:31:01,950 --> 00:31:05,310
還沒到走的時候
You're not supposed to go yet!

229
00:31:05,350 --> 00:31:07,830
可惡的東西
Infernal machine!

230
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:14,070
葛雷格 等等
Gregor. Gregor, wait!

231
00:31:14,150 --> 00:31:15,870
海倫 我試過了 出了點兒意外
Helen, I tried. There was an accident.

232
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:17,590
停不下來了 動作得快點
I can't make it stop. Hurry!

233
00:31:17,630 --> 00:31:20,990
盡全力追上來 跑起來!快點!
You can make it if you try. Run! Up those stairs. Run! Quickly!

234
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:25,230
- 等等! - 我把繩子扔給你們 跑快點!
- Wait! Wait! - I'll throw you a rope. Run quickly!

235
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:28,310
- 把繩子丟下來 跑 埃諾拉 對不起
- Throw the rope now. Run, Enola. - Slow down! Wait!

236
00:31:28,350 --> 00:31:32,310
- 把繩子丟下來 不!不! - 等等!
- Throw the rope. No! No! - Wait!

237
00:31:33,950 --> 00:31:36,110
- 葛雷格 別丟下我們! - 噢 不要
- Gregor, don't leave us! - Oh, no!

238
00:31:36,150 --> 00:31:38,310
抱 這完全是個意外
I'm sorry! It was an accident!

239
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:46,630
海倫 埃諾拉 海倫 對不起
Helen! Enola! Helen, I'm sorry!

240
00:31:55,670 --> 00:31:58,950
射下他 把他射下來
Shoot him. Shoot him.

241
00:32:25,790 --> 00:32:29,190
如果我救你出來了 那你就得帶上我們
If I let you out of here, you're taking us with you.

242
00:32:30,430 --> 00:32:32,390
沒問題
Sure.

243
00:32:34,110 --> 00:32:36,350
埃諾拉 蹲下
Enola, get down.

244
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:40,230
呆這兒 呆在這兒 蹲下來
Here. Get over here. Get down.

245
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:42,230
快點 快
Hurry! Come on!

246
00:32:45,190 --> 00:32:47,670
去把大門打開
Get the gate.

247
00:33:20,230 --> 00:33:22,190
快點
Run!

248
00:33:46,470 --> 00:33:48,390
動作快點
Hurry up!

249
00:33:48,470 --> 00:33:50,390
自殺衝鋒隊 給我上
Kamikazes. Come on!

250
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:21,110
炸了個大洞
That made a hole.

251
00:34:32,790 --> 00:34:36,230
快找 抓住那個女孩
Find her! Get the girl!

252
00:34:41,310 --> 00:34:43,390
在那邊
There!

253
00:34:50,350 --> 00:34:53,590
快 抓住那傢伙 快 滅了他
Go get that guy! Go! Kill him!

254
00:34:57,830 --> 00:35:00,190
- 哇! - 埃諾拉!
- Wow! - Enola!

255
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:13,590
- 你們倆動作太慢啦 - 到另一邊去
- You're too slow! - Run to the other side.

256
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:18,630
快點
Come on!

257
00:35:21,950 --> 00:35:26,030
抓穩了 堅持住 堅持住
Grab on! Hold on, hold on.

258
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:32,110
勾住了 我過不去
I'm stuck! I can't make it through!

259
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:34,950
放開她
Let her go!

260
00:35:35,990 --> 00:35:37,990
就讓她掉下來吧
Just drop her!

261
00:35:52,670 --> 00:35:56,470
轉那個舵輪 舵輪 轉動它
Turn the wheel. The wheel! Turn it!

262
00:35:59,430 --> 00:36:02,390
是那個 快呀 推動它
That! Come on! Push it!

263
00:36:02,470 --> 00:36:05,150
- 我在推呢 - 快!現在拉一下!
- I am! - Hurry! Now pull!

264
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:09,190
推過去!用力推過去!推過去!
Push it! Push it hard! Push it hard!

265
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:12,230
好了 好了!現在拉這個!拉它!
Okay, okay! Now pull this! Pull this!

266
00:36:12,310 --> 00:36:15,670
拉起來!快拉
Pull! Pull it! Hurry!

267
00:36:26,030 --> 00:36:29,230
埃諾拉 跳
Enola, jump.

268
00:36:31,510 --> 00:36:34,030
- 看著我 快跳 - 知道啦
- Look at me. Jump! Now! - Okay!

269
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:52,110
好了 打擾下!
Well, excuse me!

270
00:36:52,110 --> 00:36:55,550
我是不是說過攻擊結束前絕不能放任何人走?
Did I say anybody could leave before the battle was over?

271
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:57,550
- 是不是? - 是的 是的
- Did I? - No! No!

272
00:36:57,630 --> 00:37:00,110
那就行動啊 我恨死了那些帆船
Well, do somethin'. I hate sails.

273
00:37:09,350 --> 00:37:12,550
嘿 你會操作嗎?
Hey! Can you steer?

274
00:37:12,590 --> 00:37:14,550
我能相信你嗎?
Can I trust you?

275
00:37:49,190 --> 00:37:52,630
誰能告訴我 為什麼那艘船還在不停地開火
Answer me this, somebody. Why is that boat still firin'?

276
00:37:53,710 --> 00:37:56,430
- 那夥計叫啥名來著? - 查克
- What's that cousin's name? - Chuck.

277
00:37:56,470 --> 00:38:00,630
- 嘿 查克 - 他正把他的槍口拖向我們這邊
- Hey, Chuck! - He's pulling him right into us.

278
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:02,970
也許他對查克這個叫法沒反應
Maybe he doesn't answer to "Chuck."

279
00:38:02,970 --> 00:38:05,230
叫他查爾斯 查爾斯
Call him "Charles." Charles!

280
00:38:06,310 --> 00:38:10,350
讓他停下來!叫他停下來
Stop him! Stop him!

281
00:38:17,790 --> 00:38:19,790
查爾斯
Charles!

282
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:23,590
再見了 夥計們
Adios, cousins.

283
00:39:09,550 --> 00:39:11,630
她一定在這兒 繼續找
She's here somewhere. Keep lookin'.

284
00:39:11,710 --> 00:39:14,350
停止!
Stop it!

285
00:39:23,750 --> 00:39:25,570
你搞什麼鬼啊?
What you got?

286
00:39:25,570 --> 00:39:29,390
還留了幾個活口在那邊 但卻問不出什麼
Couple of heartbeats over there. Aren't sayin' much.

287
00:39:29,470 --> 00:39:31,890
如果你們有注意到這鮮紅的血
If you'll notice the arterial nature of the blood

288
00:39:31,890 --> 00:39:33,510
都是從我頭上這個窟窿流出來的
comin' from the hole in my head,

289
00:39:33,590 --> 00:39:37,870
你們就應該想到我們今天真得過得很不爽
you can assume that we're all havin' a real lousy day.

290
00:39:38,110 --> 00:39:41,790
所以現在 我要知道有紋身小女孩在哪兒
So here it is: I need to know about that tattooed girl.

291
00:39:43,430 --> 00:39:45,670
誰先說誰就能活命
First one that tells me lives.

292
00:39:45,750 --> 00:39:48,150
我看到一個女孩 我看到
I saw a girl. I saw, I saw...

293
00:39:48,150 --> 00:39:50,550
是 她身上有一個很大的紋身
It was... Sh-She had a big tattoo on her.

294
00:39:52,790 --> 00:39:55,715
你贏了 重新來
You won. Start over.

295
00:39:55,750 --> 00:39:57,910
我看到一個女孩 雖然不是很肯定
I saw a girl. I'm not sure,

296
00:39:58,150 --> 00:40:01,790
但我想她上了那艘有三個船身的船
but I think she got on that boat with three hulls.

297
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:06,250
就是那艘浪費了我1000千克汽油的船嗎
The boat that cost me a thousand G's of go-juice?

298
00:40:06,250 --> 00:40:07,390
是的 那個變種人的船
Yeah, the mute-o's boat.

299
00:40:07,470 --> 00:40:11,390
- 變種人? - 是的 他身上有一些裂縫
- Mute-o? - Yeah. He got these slits here.

300
00:40:11,430 --> 00:40:14,750
就像是魚鰓一樣
Like... Like fish gills.

301
00:40:14,830 --> 00:40:17,190
他不算是地道的人類了
He wasn't really a man.

302
00:40:17,270 --> 00:40:19,830
應該是一個偶然的進化
A fluke of evolution.

303
00:40:21,470 --> 00:40:23,750
噢 抱歉 一個偶然的
Oh, I'm sorry. A fluke of, uh...

304
00:40:23,830 --> 00:40:26,310
- 進化 - 我知道
- Evolution. - I know!

305
00:40:26,350 --> 00:40:30,270
- 不!不要 你說過不會殺我的 - 我說過那話?
- No! No, you said you wouldn't kill me! - Did I say that?

306
00:40:30,350 --> 00:40:33,430
- 有誰聽到我說過嗎? - 是的 沒錯 你說過
- Witnesses, anybody, did I? - Yes, yes, yes! You said...

307
00:40:33,510 --> 00:40:35,950
- 你確實說過 - 噢 我可能是說過
- You said it. - Oh, I may have.

308
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:39,910
可能是說過
I may have.

309
00:40:50,150 --> 00:40:53,390
給飛機加滿油 讓它出去巡邏
tank up that sky boat; send it out on patrol.

310
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:57,350
我們得睜大眼
We gotta keep an eye out...

311
00:40:57,430 --> 00:40:59,750
好好留意那個人魚怪物
for that ichthy-freak.

312
00:41:23,550 --> 00:41:25,630
你到過那兒 對吧?
You been there, haven't you?

313
00:41:30,470 --> 00:41:32,950
陸地?
Dryland?

314
00:41:33,190 --> 00:41:35,310
你知道它的方位
You know where it is.

315
00:41:36,310 --> 00:41:38,310
對 我知道它的方位
Yeah, I know where it is.

316
00:41:41,390 --> 00:41:43,950
那麼 我們要去那兒嗎?
And, uh... And we're going?

317
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:46,990
你和我可以
You and I are.

318
00:41:48,630 --> 00:41:51,750
那孩子我們得讓她下船
The kid we gotta pitch over the side.

319
00:41:53,630 --> 00:41:57,630
- 什麼? - 我的船破了
- What? - My boat's tore up.

320
00:41:57,710 --> 00:42:00,270
我剛堵上了漏洞減少了進水
I'm takin' on water.

321
00:42:00,350 --> 00:42:03,710
幸好我還有那東西能過濾二次淡化水
I'd be lucky to get half a hydro ration out of that.

322
00:42:03,750 --> 00:42:07,470
你知道 我說了我不會喝的
You know... I said I won't drink.

323
00:42:07,510 --> 00:42:09,990
可以堅持整整12天?
For 12 days?

324
00:42:11,630 --> 00:42:14,590
算了吧 最好犧牲你們其中一個
No. It's better one of you dies now...

325
00:42:14,630 --> 00:42:16,710
免得你們死得很痛苦
than both of you die slow.

326
00:42:16,790 --> 00:42:18,910
等一下 等等
Wait. Wait.

327
00:42:18,990 --> 00:42:21,550
我們救了你一命 幫助你逃出生天
We saved your life. We got you out.

328
00:42:21,590 --> 00:42:25,670
不 助我是為了幫你們自己罷了 我們算是扯平了
No, you got me out so you could get out. We're even.

329
00:42:25,750 --> 00:42:27,750
她會煮飯 也會抓魚
She can cook. She can fish.

330
00:42:27,830 --> 00:42:30,030
- 我也會 - 那我的項鏈給你 拿著
- So can I. - Then take my necklace. Take my necklace.

331
00:42:30,270 --> 00:42:32,470
- 我在下面能找到更好的 - 別 聽著
- I got better ones below. - No, look!

332
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:35,430
哦
Oh.

333
00:42:35,470 --> 00:42:38,550
在環礁基地經歷的一切後
After what you went through back there on the atoll,

334
00:42:38,630 --> 00:42:41,710
我完全明白你想這麼做的原因
I can understand why you would want to.

335
00:42:41,790 --> 00:42:43,790
但她還只是個孩子啊
But she's a child.

336
00:42:54,830 --> 00:42:57,350
那還有其他問題了嗎
Is there something else then?

337
00:43:02,670 --> 00:43:05,350
埃諾拉 到下面去
Enola! Go below.

338
00:43:06,470 --> 00:43:08,430
埃諾拉
Enola.

339
00:43:18,750 --> 00:43:21,950
是啊 你自己也說了
Yeah. You said so yourself.

340
00:43:23,910 --> 00:43:26,670
出海漂泊很長時間了
Been out there a long time.

341
00:44:12,430 --> 00:44:15,430
幾小時之前 我不過是你們眼中值得回收成泥土的傢伙
Couple hours ago, I was potential dirt to you.

342
00:44:15,510 --> 00:44:18,870
- 我們並不像那些人 - 你們沒差別
- We're not like that. - You all are.

343
00:44:24,510 --> 00:44:27,750
知道我當時真正的想法嗎?
Know what I was really thinkin'?

344
00:44:27,790 --> 00:44:30,950
為什麼我不趁自己清醒時把你們都扔下海呢
Why I don't drop both of you in my wake right now.

345
00:44:32,390 --> 00:44:34,830
我對你沒任何興趣
You got nothin' I need.

346
