I- I-I don't have it. Don't have it. Don't have it.

515
01:02:05,990 --> 01:02:10,110
已經好幾個月沒見到半個人來交意了 等等 先等等
Haven't seen neither for trade in lunars now. Wait. Wait, wait, wait.

516
01:02:13,470 --> 01:02:15,750
我確實有些能讓你改變想法東西
I do have somethin' that'll make you change your mind.

517
01:02:16,990 --> 01:02:20,630
讓你無法抗拒的東西
Somethin' that you can't pass on.

518
01:02:20,710 --> 01:02:24,990
我從一個難民環礁基地弄來的
I took it off an Atoller refugee camp.

519
01:02:25,030 --> 01:02:26,990
是整個氏族一輩子的積蓄
The life savings of the entire clan.

520
01:02:34,950 --> 01:02:37,950
紙張
Paper.

521
01:02:38,030 --> 01:02:43,590
這可是紙啊 你見過紙嗎?你看看
It's paper. Have you ever seen paper? Look at it.

522
01:02:43,670 --> 01:02:45,590
聞聞看
Smell it.

523
01:02:47,190 --> 01:02:49,470
我一直珍藏著就是為了特別交易
I been savin' it for a special trade.

524
01:02:52,590 --> 01:02:55,110
別這麼做
Don't you do it.

525
01:02:55,190 --> 01:02:58,070
我是不是找錯談判對象了啊
You know, maybe I'm talkin' to the wrong person here.

526
01:02:58,150 --> 01:03:00,270
這艘船到底是誰的?究竟是你的船還是你的呢?
Whose boat is this? Is it your boat or your boat?

527
01:03:00,510 --> 01:03:03,990
不 不 船是他的 但我們不是他的
No. No, it's his boat. But he doesn't own us.

528
01:03:11,030 --> 01:03:13,030
半小時
Half an hour.

529
01:03:13,110 --> 01:03:16,710
他瘋啦還是怎麼了
Out of his mind somethin' there.

530
01:03:16,790 --> 01:03:20,750
我用這個至少能換個半打姑娘 你知道嗎?
I got two pages in here, man! I mean, I'd get half a dozen girls with this, you know.

531
01:03:20,830 --> 01:03:23,550
就半小時
Half an hour.

532
01:03:23,590 --> 01:03:25,710
- 要不要隨你 - 別這樣
- You tradin' or not? - Don't.

533
01:03:25,790 --> 01:03:27,750
閉嘴
Shut up.

534
01:03:29,230 --> 01:03:31,310
好吧
Okay.

535
01:03:32,990 --> 01:03:35,230
不然換45分鐘跟那邊那個幼齒吧
Forty-five minutes with the wee one right there.

536
01:03:35,270 --> 01:03:37,790
我更中意調教幼齒 你該明白的?
I like to do the talkin', if you know what I mean.

537
01:03:39,590 --> 01:03:41,510
不行
No!

538
01:03:42,550 --> 01:03:45,630
好吧 快過來 來 來 來 來啊
Fair. Come, come, come, come, come!

539
01:03:45,710 --> 01:03:47,990
不 就在我的船上
No. My boat.

540
01:03:49,950 --> 01:03:53,270
- 可以 可以 好的 好的 當然沒問題 - 海倫
- Fair enough. Fair enough. Good, good, good. Aye. - Helen.

541
01:03:53,350 --> 01:03:56,950
- 坐下來 - 埃諾拉 乖乖聽他的話
- Sit down. - Enola, just do as he says.

542
01:04:43,190 --> 01:04:46,190
這對現在的我而言只算得上一小會兒
It's been a while for me now.

543
01:04:46,270 --> 01:04:49,910
但事實上 那卻又不止一小會兒
Guess it's been more than a while, actually.

544
01:04:53,070 --> 01:04:57,990
我只有半個小時 半個小時 半個小時啊
I've only got half an hour.Half an hour, half an hour, half an hour...

545
01:04:59,110 --> 01:05:01,030
對了 對了 很好
Great, great, great...

546
01:05:01,110 --> 01:05:05,910
你好美 有人這麼稱讚過你嗎?
Ooh! You're so beautiful. Aye! Anyone ever told you that?

547
01:05:05,990 --> 01:05:08,910
少來這套 你這是在幹嘛?不就是睡一覺嘛
Give me that. What are you doin'? It's just a game.

548
01:05:12,230 --> 01:05:15,230
我 我 我們剛剛只是想跟她玩玩
Oh, I, um... I, uh... We was just playin'.

549
01:05:18,350 --> 01:05:20,350
不換了
The trade's off.

550
01:05:20,430 --> 01:05:22,310
我改變主意
I changed my mind.

551
01:05:23,350 --> 01:05:26,350
你不能反悔
Well, um... Well, you can't do that.

552
01:05:26,430 --> 01:05:28,990
都已經成交了啊
I mean, a deal's a deal, eh?

553
01:05:29,030 --> 01:05:30,910
我說了反悔了
I just did.

554
01:05:31,350 --> 01:05:33,110
嘿
Hey!

555
01:05:33,190 --> 01:05:37,790
她已經是我的了 不 不 我還沒碰到她呢 不行
She's mine. Aye. No. No, no I own her. But... No.

556
01:05:37,870 --> 01:05:40,790
- 走吧 - 行啊 行啊 走吧 走吧 很好 很好
- Go on. - Get, get, get. Go, go, go. Good, good.

557
01:05:40,830 --> 01:05:45,190
別走得太遠 這耽擱不了一分鐘
But don't go too far now. This won't take but a minute.

558
01:05:50,270 --> 01:05:55,750
我恨這艘船 我恨透了這條船
I hate this boat. I hate this boat!

559
01:05:55,830 --> 01:05:58,390
你這渾球
You bastard.

560
01:06:02,750 --> 01:06:07,670
對於擁有這麼多東西的人來說你真是摳到家了
You... You're pretty stingy for a man who's got everything, aren't ya now?

561
01:06:24,230 --> 01:06:26,350
你這渾球
Ah, you bastard!

562
01:06:37,870 --> 01:06:39,910
我的船在哪兒啊?
Where's me boat?

563
01:06:41,110 --> 01:06:43,190
我的小船呢?
Where's me boat?

564
01:06:50,470 --> 01:06:52,430
帶我到船上
Help me to me boat.

565
01:06:54,030 --> 01:06:57,150
我的船
Ow! Me boat.

566
01:06:58,150 --> 01:07:00,030
我的船
Me boat.

567
01:07:29,030 --> 01:07:30,950
想幹嘛 別!
What the... No!

568
01:07:33,270 --> 01:07:35,510
用這個根本抓不到任何東西 就是個廢物
Never catch anything with this. It's useless.

569
01:07:41,390 --> 01:07:45,990
聽著 我道歉 你說得很對 那竿子是廢物
Look, I'm sorry. You were right about the pole.

570
01:07:47,270 --> 01:07:49,830
你說得對是對 但我們還是得吃東西啊
You were right, but we have to eat.

571
01:07:55,430 --> 01:07:57,390
嘿 別裝聾作啞的
Now I know you can hear me!

572
01:07:57,470 --> 01:08:00,990
我們可以自己抓魚來吃 但至少你得告訴我們該怎麼做
Now we can fish for ourselves. You show us what to do.

573
01:08:01,070 --> 01:08:03,310
你要知道 即使是你也要吃東西的
You must know how. Even you gotta eat!

574
01:08:03,390 --> 01:08:05,870
你們倆乖乖給我坐著
You just sit there.

575
01:08:29,350 --> 01:08:32,310
- 什麼玩意?... - 我不知道
- What... - I don't know.

576
01:09:08,190 --> 01:09:10,150
滿足了?
Happy now?

577
01:09:28,270 --> 01:09:30,190
你不喜歡我哼歌 對吧?
You don't like my singing, do you?

578
01:09:33,190 --> 01:09:37,150
聽海倫說你之所以討厭我唱歌是因為你不能唱
Helen says you don't like my singing 'cause you can't sing.

579
01:09:43,270 --> 01:09:45,990
- 你試著聆聽過嗎? - 聽什麼?
- Ever try and listen? - To what?

580
01:09:49,070 --> 01:09:51,270
世界之音
The sound of the world.

581
01:09:55,430 --> 01:09:58,350
- 我什麼也聽不到 - 那是因為你整天都吵個不停
- I don't hear anything. - That's because you're too loud,

582
01:09:58,430 --> 01:10:00,390
你老是動個不停
and you're movin' around all the time.

583
01:10:00,430 --> 01:10:03,230
靜下來試試
Try sittin' still.

584
01:10:03,310 --> 01:10:06,310
來顆魚眼?
Eyeball?

585
01:10:20,670 --> 01:10:22,630
我也想要他那樣的腳
I wish I had feet like his.

586
01:10:25,710 --> 01:10:27,670
也許我就能游泳了
Then maybe I could swim.

587
01:10:27,710 --> 01:10:29,430
埃諾拉
Enola.

588
01:10:33,150 --> 01:10:35,230
抱歉
Sorry.

589
01:10:39,990 --> 01:10:42,390
我之前還從來沒有見過不會游泳的人
Never met a person couldn't swim before.

590
01:10:45,230 --> 01:10:48,070
我就不會
I can't.

591
01:10:49,270 --> 01:10:51,550
別人都說我是個怪胎
People say I was weird.

592
01:10:51,590 --> 01:10:53,550
也許確如他們所說
Maybe they were right.

593
01:10:57,150 --> 01:10:59,510
也許你也確如他們所說
Maybe they were right about you too.

594
01:11:27,390 --> 01:11:29,350
埃諾拉要把這個還給你
Enola wanted to give you this.

595
01:11:33,630 --> 01:11:36,310
還有這個
And this.

596
01:11:38,430 --> 01:11:40,510
她以後不會再拿了
She won't take it again.

597
01:11:47,030 --> 01:11:49,790
你跟她長得不太像
You don't look much like her.

598
01:11:50,030 --> 01:11:51,376
我不是她的生母
Well, I'm not her mother,

599
01:11:51,376 --> 01:11:52,722
如果你想知道的是這個的話
if that's what you're asking.

600
01:11:52,722 --> 01:11:54,070
你卻視她如親生一樣
You act like it.

601
01:11:57,670 --> 01:12:00,070
她背上那些圖是什麼?
What are those marks on her back?

602
01:12:00,110 --> 01:12:02,630
沒什麼 只是好看而已
Nothing. They're just fanciful things.

603
01:12:04,110 --> 01:12:08,190
- 她畫的那些也是嗎? - 她只畫她見過得的東西
- Like what she draws? - She draws what she sees.

604
01:12:08,270 --> 01:12:11,110
她就如一面鏡子
She's like a mirror.

605
01:12:11,150 --> 01:12:13,230
大家一度認為都認為她是…
People on the atoll thought she was a...

606
01:12:15,030 --> 01:12:17,630
怪胎?
Freak?

607
01:12:17,710 --> 01:12:20,190
對
Uh-huh. Yeah.

608
01:12:20,270 --> 01:12:22,230
我卻認為她很特別
I just thought she was special.

609
01:12:29,870 --> 01:12:33,670
我並不是要給她 只是...
I'm not givin' it to her. It's just...

610
01:12:33,710 --> 01:12:35,510
借她用
A loan.

611
01:12:35,590 --> 01:12:38,550
對 我不是給她
Yeah. I'm not givin' it to her.

612
01:12:44,390 --> 01:12:47,550
陸地很美嗎?
Is Dryland beautiful?

613
01:12:49,190 --> 01:12:51,510
你會親眼所見的
You'll see.

614
01:13:17,310 --> 01:13:19,670
埃諾拉
Enola?

615
01:13:19,750 --> 01:13:21,710
埃諾拉 你在幹嘛?
Enola, what are you doing?

616
01:13:21,750 --> 01:13:25,310
- 那些怪物會殺了她的 - 它們都在睡覺
- Those monsters'll kill her! - No, they're asleep now.

617
01:13:28,590 --> 01:13:30,430
抱住我的脖子
Hands around my neck.

618
01:13:32,470 --> 01:13:35,910
讓你的手和腳在水的帶領下動起來
Let the water tell your arms and legs how to move.

619
01:13:36,230 --> 01:13:37,190
我們要潛下去 憋住呼吸
We're goin' down. Hold your breath.

620
01:15:16,670 --> 01:15:19,630
- 怎麼了? - 那是什麼?
- What is it? - What is it?

621
01:15:21,670 --> 01:15:23,750
易物交易的前哨站
Barter outpost.

622
01:15:23,830 --> 01:15:25,830
你說我們今天會到達陸地的
You said we'd get to Dryland today.

623
01:15:25,870 --> 01:15:28,950
今天 明天 都無所謂
Today. Tomorrow. What's it matter?

624
01:15:30,670 --> 01:15:32,630
我需要樹脂
I need resin.

625
01:15:42,310 --> 01:15:47,670
- 那是什麼話? - 是葡希文 他們自己的語言
- What is that? - It's PortuGreek. Their own language.

626
01:15:50,670 --> 01:15:52,910
不然就是如我所料
Or so I thought.

627
01:16:19,430 --> 01:16:21,630
呃
Ah.

628
01:16:21,710 --> 01:16:25,030
- 那就是我要的小姑娘 - 是啊
- There's my girl. - Yeah.

629
01:16:25,070 --> 01:16:28,750
您好啊 小可愛 快到我們懷抱堥荍a
Howdy, darlin'. Come on in here now.

630
01:16:58,430 --> 01:17:00,670
- 怎麼回事? - 是掠海者
- What's going on? - Smokers.

631
01:17:04,070 --> 01:17:05,990
搞什麼鬼?
What the hell?

632
01:17:09,630 --> 01:17:12,550
穿幫了快發信號
He's spotted us. Sound it!

633
01:17:12,630 --> 01:17:16,510
發信號快發信號快發信號
Sound it! Sound it! Sound it! Sound it!

634
01:17:27,550 --> 01:17:30,030
噢哦
Yahoo!

635
01:17:37,910 --> 01:17:40,910
埃諾拉
Enola!

636
01:17:52,550 --> 01:17:54,550
到右舷去馬上
Starboard side! Now!

637
01:17:55,590 --> 01:17:57,550
站到椅子上
Get in the chair!

638
01:18:03,830 --> 01:18:06,710
注意他入網了
Watch it. He's clearin' the net.

639
01:18:18,070 --> 01:18:20,190
你去掌舵
Go to the helm.

640
01:18:22,030 --> 01:18:24,510
- 把舯板打開 - 舯板?
- Get the centerboard! - Centerboard?

641
01:18:24,590 --> 01:18:27,190
- 舯板是啥? - 到底是要我做什麼?
What centerboard? I don't know what to do!

642
01:18:29,870 --> 01:18:31,950
太遲了 快過來
It's too late. Over here!

643
01:18:51,590 --> 01:18:53,550
不是吧
No!

644
01:19:09,830 --> 01:19:14,670
來福槍拿來 想做好一件事
Gimme that rifle. Boy, if you wanna do somethin' right,

645
01:19:14,750 --> 01:19:17,470
自己動手才能豐衣足食
you've got to do it yourself.

646
01:19:17,550 --> 01:19:19,510
好的
All right.

647
01:19:25,950 --> 01:19:27,910
- 我打到他了 - 我說我們...
- I winged him. - I say we load...

648
01:19:27,950 --> 01:19:31,110
快點派一艘船去逮那怪物
all the go-juice onto one boat and run the freak down.

649
01:19:31,190 --> 01:19:34,590
你派了十艘都沒能抓住他 你還想一艘就能得逞
You can't catch him in ten boats, and you wanna send just one?

650
01:19:34,630 --> 01:19:37,150
你是在講冷笑話吧
Well, I pray that you're jokin'.

651
01:19:45,670 --> 01:19:48,710
把追蹤器給我拿來
Bring me the trackers.

652
01:19:53,510 --> 01:19:55,910
他受傷了
He's hurt.

653
01:19:55,950 --> 01:19:58,270
他們不是來抓她
It's not what you think. They weren't after her.

654
01:19:58,510 --> 01:20:01,030
- 我是親眼所見 - 什麼意思?
- I saw what I saw. - What?

655
01:20:05,510 --> 01:20:07,270
別再跟我撒謊了
No more lies.

656
01:20:08,830 --> 01:20:12,030
她背上的究竟是什麼
What are the marks on her back?

657
01:20:12,070 --> 01:20:14,790
大家都說那是通往陸地的指示
People say it's the way to Dryland.

658
01:20:14,870 --> 01:20:17,550
陸地只是個神話
Dryland's a myth!

659
01:20:17,630 --> 01:20:20,590
不可能 你自己說過你知道它在哪兒的
No! You said so yourself that you know where it is.

660
01:20:20,670 --> 01:20:22,630
你說過
You did.

661
01:20:26,790 --> 01:20:29,950
你居然蠢得去相信見都沒見過的東西
You're a fool to believe in something you've never seen before.

662
01:20:30,030 --> 01:20:32,290
我不光見過 我更摸過
I've seen it. I've touched it! 

663
01:20:32,290 --> 01:20:34,550
那泥土比你帶來的更肥沃 色澤更深
Dirt that was richer and darker than yours.

664
01:20:34,590 --> 01:20:36,550
就在發現埃諾拉的那個籃子
It was in the basket we found Enola in!

665
01:20:36,590 --> 01:20:39,110
- 那根本就不存在 - 你憑什麼那麼肯定?
- It doesn't exist! - Well, how can you be so sure?

666
01:20:39,190 --> 01:20:43,950
因為我的航程早已遠過了那些夢想之地 而我卻從未見到過
Because I've sailed farther than most have dreamed, and I've never seen it.

667
01:20:45,910 --> 01:20:48,750
但你船上的那些東西呢
But the things on your boat!

668
01:20:48,830 --> 01:20:51,110
我船上的東西 指什麼?
"Things on my boat" what?

669
01:20:51,190 --> 01:20:54,710
你船上那些個沒人見過的東西
There are things on your boat that nobody has ever seen!

670
01:20:54,790 --> 01:20:56,910
像這些貝殼吶?
What are these shells?

671
01:20:56,990 --> 01:21:00,070
還有那個反光鏡啊
And that reflecting glass?

672
01:21:00,150 --> 01:21:04,630
以及那個音樂盒 那個
And th-the music box? That...

673
01:21:04,670 --> 01:21:08,270
那不是陸地來的 那是哪兒來的呢?哪兒來的?
Well, if not from Dryland, then where? Wh-Where?

674
01:21:11,150 --> 01:21:13,110
你想看陸地嗎?
You wanna see Dryland?

675
01:21:14,870 --> 01:21:16,830
你真的那麼想看嗎?
You really wanna see it?

676
01:21:18,390 --> 01:21:20,590
我就帶你到陸地
I'll take you to Dryland.

677
01:21:27,870 --> 01:21:29,870
下水
Get in.

678
01:21:35,830 --> 01:21:38,910
- 埃諾拉怎麼辦? - 這兒的空氣只夠一個人用
- Well, what about Enola? - There's only air for one.

679
01:21:38,990 --> 01:21:41,270
- 快下來 - 沒事的
- Get in the water. - It'll be all right.

680
01:21:46,990 --> 01:21:48,990
別亂來啊?
Don't touch anything.

681
01:21:53,830 --> 01:21:55,790
好了嗎?
Okay?

682
01:25:26,910 --> 01:25:28,830
真沒想到
I didn't know.

683
01:25:30,550 --> 01:25:33,510
這麼久以來
All this time...

684
01:25:33,590 --> 01:25:35,550
真沒想到
I didn't know.

685
01:25:35,590 --> 01:25:37,550
沒有人知道
Nobody does.

686
01:25:45,630 --> 01:25:47,590
我們逃得掉嗎?
Can you get us outta here?

687
01:25:47,630 --> 01:25:51,190
要我說倒是兩種可能性
I'd say there're two chances o' that.

688
01:25:51,270 --> 01:25:53,630
- 嘿! - 那就是無處可逃 無計可施
- Hey! - No way and no how.

689
01:25:53,870 --> 01:25:57,430
早就叫你請我喝一杯的 上來
Shoulda bought me that drink. Come on!

690
01:25:57,510 --> 01:25:59,350
上來 快
This way. Come on!

691
01:26:06,150 --> 01:26:08,350
首先正式地自我介紹一下
Proper introductions first.

692
01:26:09,470 --> 01:26:11,990
我就是帝剛
I'm the Deacon.

693
01:26:16,310 --> 01:26:18,670
如果不記得我這張臉了 可能是
If you don't recall the face, perhaps it's

694
01:26:18,670 --> 01:26:21,030
因為之前我的臉可並不是這個樣子
'cause I didn't always look like this.

695
01:26:24,150 --> 01:26:27,670
我一直在猜她到底躲在哪
Now, ahem, I suspect she's somewhere real close.

696
01:26:27,910 --> 01:26:30,790
為了找到她 我們不得不痛心地拆了這艘船
So we can tear this boat apart lookin' for her,

697
01:26:30,790 --> 01:26:33,670
但是我更希望有人能告訴我她躲在哪兒
but I'd rather somebody tell me where she is.

698
01:26:33,710 --> 01:26:36,550
誰先說誰就能活下來
And the first one that does that, lives.

699
01:26:36,630 --> 01:26:41,110
而亞軍就 事實上 壓根就不會有亞軍
And the runner-up... Well, actually, there are no runners-up.

700
01:26:43,630 --> 01:26:46,310
哦 親愛的喬 這可是我的最愛
Oh, sweet Joe, I love this part.

701
01:26:46,390 --> 01:26:49,270
自己挑吧 第一名還是第二 生還是死
Choose 'em. One, two. Live or die.

702
01:26:50,670 --> 01:26:53,990
就我個人而言
You know, personally,

703
01:26:54,030 --> 01:26:57,030
我更喜歡留下你來好好享用
I'd rather shoot the sperm-of-the-devil here.

704
01:26:57,070 --> 01:27:00,230
但就算你知道
Huh? But you know somethin'?

705
01:27:00,310 --> 01:27:02,710
我想你也不會告訴我的 對嗎?
I don't think you're gonna tell me, are ya?

706
01:27:02,950 --> 01:27:04,710
真遺憾
Huh? Too bad.

707
01:27:06,030 --> 01:27:09,430
好了 有什麼要說的嗎
Come on, eh? What do you say?

708
01:27:09,510 --> 01:27:11,430
她又不是你同類
She's not your kind.

709
01:27:12,990 --> 01:27:15,390
你根本就沒有同類吧
You don't even have a kind.

710
01:27:15,470 --> 01:27:19,550
你告訴了他 他還是會殺了我們倆
If you say it, he'll still kill us both.

711
01:27:24,030 --> 01:27:25,990
咱就別相互為難彼此了
Let's not get ahead of ourselves.

712
01:27:28,030 --> 01:27:29,950
如果你不說
If you don't tell me,

713
01:27:30,030 --> 01:27:32,470
我以波塞冬海神之名起誓我一定燒了你的船
I swear to Poseidon I will torch your boat.

714
01:27:39,150 --> 01:27:42,510
提醒我一下 之前遇到這種情況時是怎麼做的來著?
Refresh my memory. What happens when neither of 'em talks?

715
01:27:42,590 --> 01:27:45,470
- 從沒遇到過 - 從沒遇到過
- Never happened before. - Never happened before.

716
01:27:45,550 --> 01:27:48,230
好啊
All right!

717
01:27:48,270 --> 01:27:53,350
如果他們不說 就幹掉他們
If they won't tell us where she is, do 'em! Both of 'em! Kill 'em now!

718
01:27:53,390 --> 01:27:56,350
- 不要 - 不要
- No! - No!

719
01:27:56,390 --> 01:27:58,350
真好騙 把她帶過來
So gullible! Bring her here.

720
01:28:00,990 --> 01:28:03,590
- 到手了 - 不 放開她!
Take and ye shall receive! - No! Leave her!

721
01:28:03,670 --> 01:28:06,390
今天的布道就到此結束啦
So ends your daily sermonette!

722
01:28:06,430 --> 01:28:10,310
我們只要能搞懂這個地圖就成了 把她倒過來衣服揭開
All we gotta do is figure out this map. Turn her upside down.

723
01:28:10,390 --> 01:28:13,670
- 你看得明白嗎? - 不明白
- Does that mean anything to you? - No.

724
01:28:13,710 --> 01:28:17,310
回帝斯號去慢慢琢磨 兄弟們 打道回府了
We'll figure it out back at the 'Deez. Back at the 'Deez, boys.

725
01:28:17,390 --> 01:28:19,670
好好看著她 小心點
Careful with her. Careful with her!

726
01:28:19,750 --> 01:28:21,630
- 他們呢? - 兩個都幹掉
- What about them? - Do 'em both.

727
01:28:21,710 --> 01:28:24,350
船也燒了
Torch the boat.

728
01:28:27,750 --> 01:28:30,670
我們得潛下水
We have to go under!

729
01:28:31,790 --> 01:28:34,670
不行 我不像你能在水下呼吸
No, I can't breath like you!

730
01:28:34,750 --> 01:28:36,670
我可以讓我們倆同時呼吸
I'll breathe for both of us.

731
01:29:03,390 --> 01:29:05,310
海倫
Helen!

732
01:29:07,350 --> 01:29:12,790
海倫 救救我!海倫 海倫
Helen, help! Helen! Helen!

733
01:29:44,150 --> 01:29:46,070
我的船
My boat.

734
01:29:55,470 --> 01:29:57,390
埃諾拉
Enola.

735
01:29:59,750 --> 01:30:02,550
這算什麼?把她的鐐銬解開
What is this? Get those chains off her.

736
01:30:02,630 --> 01:30:05,590
怎麼?我們是野蠻人嗎?
What are we, barbarians here?

737
01:30:05,630 --> 01:30:08,150
我的老天啊 太沒人性了
Goodness gracious. Sakes alive.

738
01:30:08,190 --> 01:30:10,590
快滾 滾出去 你這個又肥又討厭的東西
Come on. Outta here, you big, nasty animal, you!

739
01:30:12,310 --> 01:30:14,630
Well rub-a-dub-dub.

740
01:30:16,550 --> 01:30:19,910
要過來坐我的大腿上嗎?
You wanna come over here and sit on my lap?

741
01:30:20,110 --> 01:30:22,710
不要?
No? Ahem.

742
01:30:22,790 --> 01:30:25,790
來根香煙如何?
How 'bout a cigarette?

743
01:30:25,870 --> 01:30:29,390
抽根香煙快樂似神僊
Nothin' like a good smoke if you miss your mom.

744
01:30:29,430 --> 01:30:31,390
多小開始抽都沒關係
Never too young to start.

745
01:30:32,910 --> 01:30:36,390
不要 好吧 有些東西我知道你一定喜歡
No. Well, I got somethin' right here I know you'd like.

746
01:30:38,190 --> 01:30:40,630
你很喜歡畫畫 對吧?
Like to draw, don't you? Huh?

747
01:30:42,630 --> 01:30:46,790
他們都可以給你
Huh? Now they're yours...

748
01:30:46,870 --> 01:30:51,230
只要你幫我一個忙 行嗎?
if you help me with just one problem, all right?

749
01:30:54,270 --> 01:30:57,750
你背上的那個紋身
Now, ahem... Now that tattoo on your back... Ahem.

750
01:30:59,510 --> 01:31:03,910
我聽說那似乎是一份地圖是嗎 聽說那其實是地圖
I've been told that, uh... that's actually a map?

751
01:31:07,230 --> 01:31:09,550
那是通向陸地的指示
It's the way to Dryland.

752
01:31:09,590 --> 01:31:11,550
看來我們找到地方了
Now we're gettin' someplace.

753
01:31:13,390 --> 01:31:16,190
你能教我怎麼看嗎?
Could you teach me how to read that?

754
01:31:18,950 --> 01:31:20,870
功虧一簣啊
Setback.

755
01:31:23,230 --> 01:31:27,310
那你曾聽你的哪位朋友討論過那個紋身嗎
Well, have you ever heard any of your friends talk about it?

756
01:31:27,390 --> 01:31:32,470
比如你媽媽或者是你的寵物魚叔叔 他說過什麼嗎?
You know, like your mommy or your pet fish? Did he say anything?

757
01:31:32,550 --> 01:31:34,910
你不該嘲笑他的 他會不高興的
You shouldn't make fun of him. He wouldn't like it.

758
01:31:34,950 --> 01:31:40,510
我才不管他喜不喜歡 他弄瞎了我的一隻眼
Girl, I don't give a shit what he'd like. He took out my eye.

759
01:31:40,550 --> 01:31:46,470
如果再讓我看到他 我一定要開他的腦吸乾他的腦髓
And if I ever see him again, I'm gonna cut open his head and eat his brains!

760
01:31:46,550 --> 01:31:48,750
他會喜歡那樣嗎
You think he'd like that?

761
01:31:48,790 --> 01:31:52,630
根本殺不了他他可比你狠多了
Can't kill him. He's even meaner than you are.

762
01:31:53,630 --> 01:31:55,750
但他不在這兒
But he's not here.

763
01:31:55,830 --> 01:31:57,750
更不會來這兒
And he ain't comin'.

764
01:31:57,830 --> 01:31:59,710
所以根本沒人會來救你
And no one's gonna save you.

765
01:32:01,030 --> 01:32:02,990
他一定會來救我的 一定會
He'll come for me. He will.

766
01:32:03,030 --> 01:32:07,270
那你最好乖乖地從實招來
Then you better tell me what I wanna know

767
01:32:07,310 --> 01:32:09,470
否則他能救到的只會是個屍骨無存的你
or he can see what's left of you in a goddamn jar.

768
01:32:19,750 --> 01:32:22,030
我們死定了 對不對?
We're going to die here, aren't we?

769
01:32:41,910 --> 01:32:43,910
是嗎?
Aren't we?

770
01:32:53,390 --> 01:32:55,990
逃出環礁基地後
After the atoll,

771
01:32:56,070 --> 01:32:58,790
我曾要獻身給你
when I offered myself to you,

772
01:33:01,430 --> 01:33:03,830
你當時為什麼會拒絕呢?
why didn't you take me?

773
01:33:05,750 --> 01:33:07,670
因為你並不是真得想要我
'Cause you didn't really want me.

774
01:33:09,670 --> 01:33:12,630
你不是自願的
Not really.

775
01:35:08,470 --> 01:35:10,750
我睡了很久嗎?
Have I been asleep long?

776
01:35:16,510 --> 01:35:18,470
我做了個夢
I was dreaming.

777
01:35:20,870 --> 01:35:23,870
很奇怪
It's funny.

778
01:35:23,910 --> 01:35:26,710
我一直以為陸地是漂浮著的
I always thought Dryland floated.

779
01:35:26,750 --> 01:35:28,430
它會隨風而動 所以才那麼難找
That it drifted with the wind.

780
01:35:28,430 --> 01:35:30,110
為什麼你會如此地深信不疑
That's why it was so hard to find.

781
01:35:30,150 --> 01:35:32,550
你為什麼深信有陸地?
Why did you believe in it so much?

782
01:35:33,790 --> 01:35:36,430
因為我們根本無法在海洋中生存
Because we weren't made for the sea.

783
01:35:37,710 --> 01:35:40,910
看看我們的手和腳
Got hands... and feet.

784
01:35:40,990 --> 01:35:43,670
那是用來行走的
We're supposed to walk.

785
01:35:46,710 --> 01:35:48,630
我好想念她的聲音
I miss her sound.

786
01:35:51,070 --> 01:35:53,070
你呢?
Don't you?

787
01:35:56,630 --> 01:35:58,510
海倫
Helen!

788
01:35:58,590 --> 01:36:01,710
不 不對 不對 海倫 抬頭 你頭上
He... No, no, no. Helen, up here. Above you!

789
01:36:01,750 --> 01:36:04,230
葛雷格
Gregor!

790
01:36:08,710 --> 01:36:11,510
很機靈啊 燒了你們的船
Smart thinking to burn your boat.

791
01:36:11,590 --> 01:36:15,190
要不是看到了濃煙 我永遠都無法找到你們
Without the smoke, I never would have found you.

792
01:36:15,270 --> 01:36:17,270
和你一起的那傢伙是誰
Who's that with you?

793
01:36:17,510 --> 01:36:21,070
那個魚神?真的是你嗎?
Ichthyus Sapien, is that really you?

794
01:36:21,150 --> 01:36:25,110
我把繩子扔給你們 抓牢了 我把你們拉上來
I'll throw the rope down. You catch it. I'll help you climb up.

795
01:36:27,470 --> 01:36:30,870
海倫 埃諾拉呢?
Helen. Where's Enola?

796
01:36:30,950 --> 01:36:36,310
被掠海者抓走了 幸好有他在 我才倖免於難
Smokers took her. They'd have me too if it weren't for him.

797
01:36:36,510 --> 01:36:40,670
我的朋友 謝謝你 你非常地有人性
My friend, thank you. Very human of you.

798
01:36:42,630 --> 01:36:45,190
快把你們的東西拿上 動作快 快
Go grab your things quickly. Quickly. Come.

799
01:36:53,110 --> 01:36:55,110
看到了嗎?就在這下面
You see? Right down there.

800
01:36:55,190 --> 01:36:58,190
那是基地的一些倖存者 我們正準備重新開始
There's several of us survivors. We'll just start over again.

801
01:37:00,270 --> 01:37:02,190
你不能要求我們都去救她
You can't ask us to go get her!

802
01:37:02,270 --> 01:37:04,630
埃諾拉正是這場劫難的根源
Enola's the reason we're in all this trouble.

803
01:37:04,710 --> 01:37:09,310
反正他們又不會殺了她 他們跟我們一樣在找陸地
They don't have any reason to kill her. They need to find Dryland just like we do.

804
01:37:09,510 --> 01:37:13,310
- 毫無疑問 - 連那個浪行者都願意去了 我們怎麼能無動於衷呢
- Of course. - If the Mariner's willing to go, why not us?

805
01:37:13,550 --> 01:37:15,630
他願意就讓他去呀
If he wants to go, then let him!

806
01:37:15,710 --> 01:37:18,910
我們根本不想收留你們 你和那個女孩都是
We don't want you here! You or the girl!

807
01:37:18,990 --> 01:37:23,350
海倫 那個航海人給你的這些紙紙
Helen. The papers the Mariner brought you...

808
01:37:23,550 --> 01:37:28,070
上面的文字和紋身上面的文字是同一種語言 上面有號碼
It's the same language the tattoo is written in. They're numbers.

809
01:37:28,150 --> 01:37:31,550
- 葛雷格 你和她一樣瘋狂 - 我們不能呆在這兒
- Gregor, you're as crazy as she is! - We can't stay here!

810
01:37:31,630 --> 01:37:32,790
我們再不抓緊時間
We're wasting valuable time.

811
01:37:32,790 --> 01:37:33,950
更多的掠海者就會追來了
More Smokers will come.

812
01:37:33,950 --> 01:37:35,110
我們需要馬上轉移
We need to be moving now!

813
01:37:35,190 --> 01:37:39,630
我的朋友們 你們還不明白嗎 想要找到陸地我們就需要那個孩子
My friends, don't you see we need this child if we want to find Dryland?

814
01:37:39,710 --> 01:37:41,675
- 我才不會去呢 - 誰都不去
- I'm not goin'. - Nobody is.

815
01:37:41,710 --> 01:37:44,070
我們遠遠就看到他們的煙
We've seen their smoke on the horizon!

816
01:37:44,150 --> 01:37:46,910
- 搞懂那個是什麼了嗎? - 這些數字嗎?當然 我想我搞懂了
- Know what that is yet? - The numbers? Yes, I think I do.

817
01:37:46,990 --> 01:37:52,590
這看起來應該是過去的地理坐標 是緯度和經度
It seems to be some ancient form of geographic location: Latitude, longitude.

818
01:37:52,670 --> 01:37:57,390
不過 有點不合理 這些數字 似乎是顛倒的還是怎麼了
It doesn't make sense, though. The numbers, they seem to be backwards or something.

819
01:37:57,590 --> 01:37:59,710
- 確實是顛倒的 - 整個世界嗎?
- It's upside down. - The world?

820
01:37:59,790 --> 01:38:02,310
兩級也是顛倒的?
The poles have reversed themselves?

821
01:38:02,390 --> 01:38:04,750
我一直在勘測水下的城市
I've been mappin' the cities below.

822
01:38:07,590 --> 01:38:10,910
世界並不是在水中建起的 而是被水淹沒了
The world wasn't created in a deluge. It was covered by it.

823
01:38:10,990 --> 01:38:14,190
- 那話簡直是褻瀆神靈 - 不 那是事實
- That's blasphemy! - No, it's true.

824
01:38:14,270 --> 01:38:18,990
我親眼所見那些土地就在我們身下這片海底
I've seen it with my own eyes. There is land. It's right under our keel.

825
01:38:19,070 --> 01:38:21,110
- 根本就沒有干地 - 有些是
- None of it's dry anymore. - Some is.

826
01:38:22,710 --> 01:38:27,190
埃諾拉確實曾到過那兒 在看到她畫得那些畫之後 我很肯定
Enola's been there. I know that now. I saw what she drew.

827
01:38:27,270 --> 01:38:31,110
所以你是為了陸地找她
So that's why he's going after Enola... to find Dryland.

828
01:38:31,190 --> 01:38:33,910
我才不管陸地
I don't care about Dryland.

829
01:38:33,990 --> 01:38:36,830
真是太荒謬可笑了 要怎麼找掠海者啊
This is ridiculous. Going after the Smokers?

830
01:38:36,910 --> 01:38:39,110
他連他們打哪兒來的都不知道
He doesn't even know which direction they came from.

831
01:38:39,190 --> 01:38:44,070
- 我說讓他走吧 - 沒有他更好
- I say let him go. - We're better off without them anyway!

832
01:38:44,110 --> 01:38:47,910
只要她還活著 我就一定把她帶回來
If she's alive, I'll bring her back to you.

833
01:38:47,950 --> 01:38:52,430
得了 別管那個變種人了 海倫別 如果他帶她回來我們都會死
Forget the mute-o, Helen. If he brings her back, they'll kill us!

834
01:38:52,670 --> 01:38:56,230
我不能袖手旁觀 我們得去幫幫他 不能讓他一個人冒險
I can't stand it. We gotta go help him. I can't ask him to do this alone.

835
01:38:56,310 --> 01:39:00,310
噢 放心吧 親愛的 你想去的話簡單得多
Oh, don't worry, my dear. You're not going to have to.

836
01:39:06,230 --> 01:39:09,190
你們搞懂紋身的涵義了嗎?
You got that tattoo figured out yet?

837
01:39:09,230 --> 01:39:11,910
如果再平整點就容易多了 最好又大又平整
It would be easier if it was flat... big and flat.

838
01:39:11,950 --> 01:39:14,870
- 這得攤平了來看 - 你到底想幹嘛?
- It needs to be flat. - What you got in mind?

839
01:39:14,910 --> 01:39:19,190
最好能從她背上割下來 就可以攤平了 甚至裱起來
Well, you cut it off her back. You stretch it, mount it.

840
01:39:19,270 --> 01:39:22,950
- 我們就能慢慢研究了 - 把她帶下去等我叫她
- Give us a proper look. - Take her down below until I holler.

841
01:39:23,030 --> 01:39:25,230
偉大的喬 就要到頭了
Saint Joe, we're close.

842
01:39:27,470 --> 01:39:29,910
在經歷了幾世紀的屈辱之後
After centuries of shame.

843
01:41:00,270 --> 01:41:03,950
- 他們開始有點暴躁了 - 聽出來了
- They're gettin' ugly. - Don't I know it.

844
01:41:04,812 --> 01:41:06,812
可以開始了 兄弟
Announce me, cousin.

845
01:41:10,932 --> 01:41:12,972
注意了 他來了
Hey. Here he is.

846
01:41:13,012 --> 01:41:14,972
帝剛
Deacon!

847
01:41:15,052 --> 01:41:17,652
熱情點 兄弟姐妹們起來
Rise up, brothers and sisters.

848
01:41:19,212 --> 01:41:22,732
睜開你們的雙眼打開胸襟
Turn your eyes and open your hearts...

849
01:41:22,812 --> 01:41:25,172
你們仁慈的佈施者
to your humble benefactor,

850
01:41:25,252 --> 01:41:29,092
你們靈魂的引導者 命運的依托者
your spiritual shepherd and dictator for life,

851
01:41:29,172 --> 01:41:32,172
帝斯號的帝剛
the Deacon of the 'Deez.

852
01:41:53,812 --> 01:41:56,892
- 當心! - 是我的!是我的!
- Look out! - It's mine! It's mine!

853
01:42:03,612 --> 01:42:06,892
- 帝剛 - 哇
- Deacon! - Wahoo!

854
01:42:06,972 --> 01:42:12,772
孩子們 我可愛的孩子們
Children. Children of the provider.

855
01:42:12,852 --> 01:42:16,732
帝斯號的好船民 安靜下來聽我說
Citizens of the good ship. Please now, hear me speak.

856
01:42:20,772 --> 01:42:23,812
- 我見到了一個幻象 - 我們已經受夠了你的那些幻象了
- I've had a vision. - Yeah, we're tired of your visions!

857
01:42:23,892 --> 01:42:26,172
你對我們許諾過的土地在哪兒呢
What about the land you promised us?

858
01:42:26,252 --> 01:42:29,052
是啊!是啊
Yeah! Yeah!

859
01:42:29,132 --> 01:42:31,252
你們對信仰太不堅定了
Oh ye of little faith.

860
01:42:31,332 --> 01:42:33,732
我看到的這個幻象如此美好
I've had a vision so great...

861
01:42:33,772 --> 01:42:37,132
美好到讓我感激涕零
that as it came to me, I wept.

862
01:42:37,172 --> 01:42:41,252
- 讓我以為那只是南柯一夢 - 這不是波恩的摩托艇嗎?
- And in this splenditudinous figment of wonder, - Is that Bone's ride?

863
01:42:41,332 --> 01:42:43,412
- 座位上是血跡嗎 - 我見到的
- Is that blood on the seat? - I saw...

864
01:42:43,652 --> 01:42:47,372
你知不知道我看到了什麼
And you know what it is that I saw.

865
01:42:47,452 --> 01:42:51,332
我看到...陸地
I saw... the land.

866
01:43:24,452 --> 01:43:26,732
霍斯 是你嗎?
Horse, that you?

867
01:43:31,332 --> 01:43:34,412
慢慢的開進來 別浪費時間
Look, just bring it in slow, okay? I don't have all day.

868
01:43:34,492 --> 01:43:37,972
霍斯
Horse!

869
01:43:38,052 --> 01:43:40,452
慢慢開進來
Just bring it up slow.

870
01:43:41,492 --> 01:43:44,452
慢慢開進來!
I said slow!

871
01:43:49,092 --> 01:43:53,252
你不應該這樣 你會惹麻煩
Shouldn't be doing that. You're gonna get in trouble.

872
01:43:53,332 --> 01:43:55,492
是啊 是啊
Ha. That's right.

873
01:43:55,732 --> 01:43:59,772
而你沒有害怕 因為你在期盼著你那可愛的怪物叔叔來救你
You're not afraid. You've got your pet freak comin' to rescue you.

874
01:43:59,852 --> 01:44:04,332
他才不是怪物呢 他隨時都能要了你的命
He's not a freak, and he can take you anytime.

875
01:44:04,372 --> 01:44:08,452
他殺人無數 冷血無情 更不會心慈手軟
He's killed dozens of people, and he doesn't have any mercy or anything.

876
01:44:08,532 --> 01:44:10,812
他連小女孩都殺
He even kills little girls.

877
01:44:12,532 --> 01:44:14,172
難道我們就會嗎
Haven't we all?

878
01:44:16,252 --> 01:44:18,212
該死的
Shit.

879
01:44:18,292 --> 01:44:20,452
是霍斯
It's Horse.

880
01:44:21,892 --> 01:44:24,332
- 去找他 去找他 - 快
- Find him. Find him! - Come on!

881
01:44:24,412 --> 01:44:28,812
是的!是的!是的!
Yes! Yes! Yes!

882
01:44:28,892 --> 01:44:32,412
- 快來 - 有點緊張了 是嗎?
- Come on. - Gettin' nervous, aren't you?

883
01:44:36,852 --> 01:44:38,772
我不會緊張
I don't get nervous.

884
01:44:40,052 --> 01:44:42,492
如果有河 我們就建壩蓄水
And if there's a river, we'll dam it.

885
01:44:42,572 --> 01:44:47,092
如果有樹 我們就大興土木
And if there's a tree, we'll ram it.

886
01:44:47,172 --> 01:44:50,252
因為此刻我說的可是發展
'Cause I'm talkin' progress here.

887
01:44:50,332 --> 01:44:53,372
是的 我說的是開拓
Yes, sir. I'm talkin' development.

888
01:44:53,412 --> 01:44:57,452
- 是的 - 因為我們馬上就能盡情地舔吸
- Yeah! - For we shall suck and savor...

889
01:44:57,492 --> 01:45:02,052
陸地的沁人芬芳
the sweet flavor of Dryland.

890
01:45:02,092 --> 01:45:03,972
你的臉已經都紅了
Face is all red.

891
01:45:04,052 --> 01:45:09,132
海倫說過如果有人的臉紅得已經成了關公那樣
Helen said with anybody that has a face that red,

892
01:45:09,172 --> 01:45:11,332
那他不是曬得太久就是喝多了
he's had too much sun or too much to drink.

893
01:45:11,412 --> 01:45:14,432
行了 我受夠了 看我不毀了你的小臉蛋兒
All right, that's it. I'm gonna burn your face.

894
01:45:14,432 --> 01:45:15,452
時間剛剛好
Almost time.

895
01:45:15,532 --> 01:45:19,572
- 怎麼了? - 只不過是剛剛聊起了她朋友
- What's up? - We're just talkin' about our friend.

896
01:45:22,052 --> 01:45:24,932
- 他叫什麼名字? - 她沒有名字
- What's his name? - He doesn't have a name.

897
01:45:25,012 --> 01:45:27,492
所以死神無法找到他
So death can't find him.

898
01:45:32,932 --> 01:45:36,852
他無親無故 沒有任何後顧之憂
Doesn't have a home or people to care for.

899
01:45:36,932 --> 01:45:39,852
他渾身是膽 無所畏懼
He's not afraid of anything, men least of all.

900
01:45:39,932 --> 01:45:43,412
他就像颶風一樣強大而迅猛
He's fast and strong like a big wind.

901
01:45:43,492 --> 01:45:46,852
在水下他更是來去自如
He can hear a hundred miles and see a hundred miles underwater.

902
01:45:46,932 --> 01:45:50,972
他能躲在太陽陰影下
He can hide in the shadow of the noon sun.

903
01:45:51,012 --> 01:45:54,932
他可以潛伏在你身後 你死了都不知道
He could be right behind you, and you won't even know it 'til you're dead!

904
01:45:57,412 --> 01:45:59,412
讓你的嘴歇歇
Give it a rest.

905
01:46:00,852 --> 01:46:02,852
他會來救我的 一定會
He'll come for me. He will.

906
01:46:02,892 --> 01:46:05,412
- 我們就是開拓先鋒 - 是嗎?
- We are the people... - Yeah?

907
01:46:05,492 --> 01:46:09,012
- 希望如此 - 這是神的恩澤
- Well, I hope he does. - The Lord's creation.

908
01:46:10,252 --> 01:46:12,172
記住你說過這句話
Remember you said that.

909
01:46:13,332 --> 01:46:16,132
瞧瞧我們
Look at us.

910
01:46:16,172 --> 01:46:18,852
- 好好看看今天還在這堛漣畯 - 是的
- Look at us here today. - Yeah!

911
01:46:18,932 --> 01:46:22,452
陸地不僅僅是我們的夢之地
Dryland is not just our destination,

912
01:46:22,492 --> 01:46:24,572
也是我們的命運
but it is our destiny!

913
01:46:34,092 --> 01:46:36,492
快去找他 把她找出來!
Find him. Find him!

914
01:46:36,532 --> 01:46:38,652
我該怎麼找到
How can I find...

915
01:46:38,892 --> 01:46:41,012
這片樂土
this glorious place?

916
01:46:42,052 --> 01:46:44,892
他對我說
And he said to me:

917
01:46:44,932 --> 01:46:48,892
你將遇見一個孩子
"A child shall lead you."

918
01:46:50,332 --> 01:46:52,412
一個孩子
A child.

919
01:46:52,492 --> 01:46:54,892
- 看哪 - 是時候了
- And behold! - It's time.

920
01:46:54,972 --> 01:46:58,012
我們的救星
The instrument of our salvation!

921
01:47:05,452 --> 01:47:07,972
我們迷途上的嚮導
Our guide in the wild.

922
01:47:08,052 --> 01:47:10,372
黑暗堛獄滽餈O
Our beacon in the darkness.

923
01:47:10,412 --> 01:47:12,372
把她的背轉過來 諾德
Turn her around, Nord.

924
01:47:12,412 --> 01:47:15,252
她已經給我展示了路徑
She has shown me the path!

925
01:47:19,652 --> 01:47:23,172
在最神聖的時刻來臨之際
And before the holy-most moment is upon us,

926
01:47:23,252 --> 01:47:26,652
讓我們為了偉大的老喬徹底瘋狂一把
let's sacrifice one to old Saint Joe.

927
01:47:29,972 --> 01:47:33,452
把我們這蛈p廢鐵的破船開動起來 全速前進
And let's get this tub of shit up to speed.

928
01:47:39,532 --> 01:47:41,492
Yep.

929
01:48:19,532 --> 01:48:21,452
快劃
Pull!

930
01:48:21,532 --> 01:48:24,252
- 快劃 - 快劃
- Pull! - Pull!

931
01:48:24,292 --> 01:48:26,412
- 快劃 - 快劃
- Pull. - Pull!

932
01:48:41,012 --> 01:48:42,812
Ow.

933
01:48:46,412 --> 01:48:49,652
- 我們要往哪個方向劃? - 我他媽的也毫無頭緒
- So which way we rowin'? - I don't have a goddamn clue.

934
01:48:49,692 --> 01:48:51,652
別緊張
Don't worry.

935
01:48:51,732 --> 01:48:54,692
等他們察覺被騙時起碼也過了一個月了
They'll row for a month before they figure out I'm fakin' it.

936
01:48:54,732 --> 01:48:57,492
但是為什麼呢
But, um, wh-wh...

937
01:48:57,532 --> 01:49:00,652
你想知道實情 不能告訴這些人
Oh, you want details. Well, I'm not tellin' these savages...

938
01:49:00,692 --> 01:49:03,012
我們還沒搞懂地圖
that we haven't solved the map yet.

939
01:49:03,092 --> 01:49:08,452
我向他們保證有結果 我會不擇手段得到結果的
I promised them results, and I'll get 'em if I gotta cut 'em out of her goddamn back.

940
01:49:09,772 --> 01:49:13,212
那是誰?那是誰?
Who is that? Who is that?

941
01:49:14,332 --> 01:49:16,732
也許是個划槳的後備吧?
Maybe one of the spare rowers?

942
01:49:24,652 --> 01:49:27,412
你怎麼不去划槳呢?
Why aren't you rowin'?

943
01:49:36,092 --> 01:49:38,132
- 是他 - 確實是他
- It's him. - It is him.

944
01:49:39,492 --> 01:49:42,212
你們麻煩可大了
You guys are in so much trouble.

945
01:49:45,092 --> 01:49:49,412
真的想不到 是那個魚人
Well, I'll be damned. It's the gentleman guppy.

946
01:49:49,452 --> 01:49:53,252
他好像洗不掉的狗屎
You know, he's like a turd that won't flush.

947
01:49:53,332 --> 01:49:56,052
把那小姑娘給我
I want the girl.

948
01:49:58,412 --> 01:50:03,532
知道嗎?我以為你只是很蠢 老兄
You know, I thought you were stupid, friend.

949
01:50:03,612 --> 01:50:06,532
不過我確實太低估你了
But I underestimated you.

950
01:50:06,612 --> 01:50:09,612
你簡直就是個低能兒
You're a total freakin' retard.

951
01:50:12,812 --> 01:50:16,172
我只要那個女孩兒
I want the girl. That's all.

952
01:50:16,212 --> 01:50:20,892
哦 在這荒涼殘敗的地球上 你憑什麼認為你辦得到?
Well, what on this screwed-up Earth makes you think you're gonna get her?

953
01:50:29,292 --> 01:50:31,252
你知道這是什麼嗎?
You know what this is?

954
01:50:35,532 --> 01:50:38,092
我丟下去你就毀了
I drop it, you burn.

955
01:50:38,132 --> 01:50:41,932
- 大家都會毀了 - 等等 等等 先等等
- We all burn. - Now wait, wait, wait, wait.

956
01:50:42,172 --> 01:50:45,812
都別衝動
Ahem. Let's not do anything rash here.

957
01:50:45,892 --> 01:50:49,212
你確定她真的值得你這麼做嗎?
I mean, uh, are you sure she's worth all this?

958
01:50:49,292 --> 01:50:52,412
她總是嘮叨個沒完沒了 從不閉嘴
She never does stop talkin'. She never shuts up.

959
01:50:52,492 --> 01:50:54,772
- 我清楚得很 - 那你是為什麼?
- I noticed. - What is it then?

960
01:50:54,852 --> 01:50:57,252
是為了地圖?
Huh? It's the map.

961
01:50:58,692 --> 01:51:01,452
她是我的朋友
She's my friend.

962
01:51:01,532 --> 01:51:04,332
我真是感動得熱淚直流
Golly gee. A single tear rolls down my cheek.

963
01:51:04,412 --> 01:51:07,332
你居然要為了你的朋友準備慷慨就義
I mean, you're gonna die for your friend.

964
01:51:08,732 --> 01:51:10,652
如果真有必要的話
If it comes to that.

965
01:51:12,892 --> 01:51:15,152
只不是虛張聲勢罷了 我要殺了他
He's bluffing. I'll kill him.

966
01:51:15,152 --> 01:51:17,412
他不是虛張聲勢 他從不會那麼做
He's not bluffing. He never bluffs.

967
01:51:17,492 --> 01:51:18,652
給我閉嘴
Shut up!

968
01:51:19,932 --> 01:51:25,212
我打賭你絕不會扔的 我的朋友
I don't... l-l... I don't think you're gonna drop that torch, my friend.

969
01:51:25,292 --> 01:51:28,852
- 為什麼? - 因為你又不是瘋子
- Why not? - Because you're not crazy.

970
01:51:32,452 --> 01:51:35,292
不
No!

971
01:51:42,252 --> 01:51:44,852
哦 真是感謝上帝
Oh, thank God.

972
01:52:01,812 --> 01:52:04,212
當心
Look out!

973
01:52:04,252 --> 01:52:06,692
逮住他
Get him!

974
01:52:06,732 --> 01:52:10,332
快點 可惡
Let's go, goddamn it!

975
01:52:10,412 --> 01:52:15,012
別淨站著 給我上
Don't just stand there! Kill somethin'!

976
01:52:18,332 --> 01:52:20,292
這就是你偉大的幻景嗎?
Was this your big vision?

977
01:52:28,852 --> 01:52:32,812
我一直渴望能開開這玩意兒
Oh, yeah! I've always wanted to drive this monster.

978
01:52:36,052 --> 01:52:39,372
是他 在那
There he is! There he is!

979
01:52:42,452 --> 01:52:44,732
在那
That's him! There!

980
01:52:57,652 --> 01:53:01,332
不 放手
No! Let go!

981
01:53:10,892 --> 01:53:13,412
放手
Let go!

982
01:53:16,732 --> 01:53:19,372
- 放手 放手 - 飛行員
- Let me go! Let go! - Pilot!

983
01:53:19,452 --> 01:53:21,812
- 飛行員 - 放了我
- Pilot! - Let me go!

984
01:53:21,892 --> 01:53:23,812
放了我!
Let go!

985
01:53:23,892 --> 01:53:25,852
放了我!
Let go-o-o-o!

986
01:53:28,292 --> 01:53:31,012
你乖乖呆在水下就沒事了
You should've stayed underwater.

987
01:53:40,852 --> 01:53:45,292
你知道怎麼駕駛飛機嗎?幸好我懂 真慶幸對吧
Now you know how to fly an airplane? You're lucky I do.

988
01:53:45,332 --> 01:53:48,332
別這樣 給我聽話點兒
Ow! Now you stop it! You behave yourself now!

989
01:55:20,772 --> 01:55:22,692
它正在下沉
It's going down.

990
01:55:22,772 --> 01:55:27,892
- 你能看見它在下沉 - 葛雷格 降到那艘船上方
- You can see it sinking. - Gregor, bring us right down on top of it.

991
01:55:27,972 --> 01:55:30,092
- 快點 葛雷格 - 別擔心
- Hurry, Gregor! - Don't worry.

992
01:55:30,172 --> 01:55:32,092
快點
Hurry.

993
01:55:43,932 --> 01:55:47,052
埃諾拉 快上來
Enola! Up here!

994
01:55:47,132 --> 01:55:49,092
抓住繩子
Grab on!

995
01:55:54,172 --> 01:55:56,132
他們倆都抓住了嗎
Are they on yet?

996
01:55:59,652 --> 01:56:02,452
- 怎麼回事兒? - 不知道
- What is it? - I don't know!

997
01:56:02,492 --> 01:56:04,172
不
No!

998
01:56:13,572 --> 01:56:18,932
抓到你了 我要好好地收拾你一頓
Gotcha! I'm gonna rip your cute little lungs out.

999
01:56:33,172 --> 01:56:35,772
用力 差不多了
Pull! Almost.

1000
01:57:14,812 --> 01:57:16,572
不
No!

1001
01:57:16,652 --> 01:57:19,572
不 埃諾拉
No! Enola!

1002
01:57:20,932 --> 01:57:23,252
偉大的喬啊 這一桿進洞真漂亮啊
Saint Joe. Hole in one.

1003
01:57:23,332 --> 01:57:27,172
- 海倫 - 不 埃諾拉 - 海倫
- Helen! - No! Enola! - Helen!

1004
01:57:27,212 --> 01:57:29,932
嘿!嘿
Hey! Hey!

1005
01:57:36,572 --> 01:57:40,612
哦 不 快想辦法啊 該怎麼辦
Ohh. Oh, no! Quick! What are we gonna do?

1006
01:57:43,892 --> 01:57:46,332
把這頭綁緊
Tie this off.

1007
01:57:49,852 --> 01:57:52,692
- 快點 - 綁緊這頭
- Hurry! - Tie it!

1008
01:57:57,172 --> 01:57:59,772
- 好了 - 噢
- Got it! - Ah!

1009
01:58:12,652 --> 01:58:15,092
快拉他們上來
Get 'em up now.

1010
01:58:25,172 --> 01:58:28,692
- 當然 北是南 - 什麼
- Of course! North is south. - What?

1011
01:58:28,772 --> 01:58:32,092
- 南是北 - 我會游泳了
- South is north. - I was swimming.

1012
01:58:32,132 --> 01:58:34,332
- 我看到了 - 我的朋友們
- I saw. - My friends.

1013
01:58:34,412 --> 01:58:36,612
朋友們 快來看看
My friends, look.

1014
01:58:36,692 --> 01:58:39,052
只要我測出來太陽高度角
If I take a bearing from the sun

1015
01:58:39,052 --> 01:58:41,412
再顛倒一下埃諾拉背上的那些數據
and reverse the coordinates on Enola's back,

1016
01:58:43,612 --> 01:58:46,772
那麼 陸地就應該是在那個方向
then Dryland is that way!

1017
02:00:48,132 --> 02:00:51,132
是淡水
It's fresh!

1018
02:00:51,212 --> 02:00:53,892
是淡水 全是淡水
All of this! It's fresh!

1019
02:01:01,092 --> 02:01:03,052
不!
No!

1020
02:01:07,492 --> 02:01:09,932
哇哦
Whoo! Whoo!

1021
02:01:10,012 --> 02:01:12,292
我發現了點東西
I found something!

1022
02:01:25,012 --> 02:01:28,492
也許我們應該讓他們入土為安
Maybe we should put them under the dirt.

1023
02:01:28,572 --> 02:01:30,492
我想那是他們的風俗
I think it was their way.

1024
02:01:32,892 --> 02:01:34,892
他們一定早就知道自己將不久於人世了
They must have known they were dying.

1025
02:02:05,412 --> 02:02:07,332
我到家了
I'm home.

1026
02:02:18,292 --> 02:02:20,892
- 航海人在哪? - 在外面
- Where's the Mariner? - He was outside.

1027
02:02:26,212 --> 02:02:28,892
等等 先等等!我想讓你看看這個
Wait. Wait! I want to show you this.

1028
02:03:41,332 --> 02:03:44,052
這可能是你有生以來第一次隻字不說吧?
First time in your life you got nothin' to say?

1029
02:03:58,932 --> 02:04:01,372
埃諾拉 我不得不馬上離開
Enola, I have to go now.

1030
02:04:01,452 --> 02:04:03,412
但你曾為了我去而復返
But you came back for me.

1031
02:04:05,492 --> 02:04:07,452
我喜歡你
I like you.

1032
02:04:12,572 --> 02:04:14,532
你為什麼要走?
Why are you leaving?

1033
02:04:17,372 --> 02:04:21,092
- 我不屬於這 我屬於外面的世界 - 你屬於這
- I don't belong here. I belong out there. - You belong here.

1034
02:04:24,372 --> 02:04:27,292
呆在這兒讓我覺得很彆扭 因為一切都是靜止的
It's too strange here. It doesn't move right.

1035
02:04:27,332 --> 02:04:30,172
海倫說那只不過是還沒有適應腳踏實地的感覺罷了
Helen said that it's only land sickness.

1036
02:04:31,372 --> 02:04:34,972
我們都有這種感覺 但很快就能適應了
We're all feeling it. It'll go away soon.

1037
02:04:35,052 --> 02:04:36,972
不只是如此
It's more than that.
